{"tid":2057681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★轉數快新騙案   扮過錯錢要求「還款」","createTime":"2020-06-09T14:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T14:12:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":103,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"ef24d55259adcca5a0598210f555c430398784bf","tid":2057681,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"有轉數快用戶收到騙徒偽造的 SMS 通知，內容為平時轉數快成功過數的通知訊息，如過數款項、交易編號、日期、時間和查詢電話等，而查詢電話更為真實的中國銀行（香港）電話號碼，令事主以為自己收到了騙徒轉帳的款項。之後騙徒會 Whatsapp 事主，訛稱過錯錢令事主把誤以為收到的款項「發還」給騙徒，更會講出用戶的姓名簡寫，以增加說服力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/hkicl01-357x580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fhkicl01-357x580.jpg&h=1a17ed85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n估計騙徒先在轉數快系統中隨機輸入電話號碼，以確認對方有沒有轉數快帳號，以及知道持有帳號用戶的姓名簡寫。只要有用戶只根據 SMS 短訊和騙徒的 Whatsapp 訊息便信以為真，就會跌入騙局，故若要讀者收到類似訊息，應先查看自己的帳號有沒有收到相關的款項，再作行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/06/09/fps-internet-fraud/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F09%2Ffps-internet-fraud%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xeln8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=679a00b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/06/09/fps-internet-fraud/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"76763c7ae333daa71d68a794b10cc10017ca0ab9","tid":2057681,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee31a6e4df6d104b1e400d7c349ebead9c12cc8","tid":2057681,"uid":213877,"like":104,"dislike":3,"score":101,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T